text: pitabrakd nasa karpipheaksaea knea daoyosngat noh ku mk pi shai tn daembi thveu aoy banda anak mean chomnue meantoukkh pruoy khn del vea minban thveu aoy puokke mean krohthnak laey louhtrate meankar anounhnhat pi a l laoh . haey champoh a l laoh temuoyokt del banda anak mean chomnue brakl kar touk chetd
